                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                <date>5 September<add>?</add> 1860</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>My dear <addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My sister mentioned to me in her<lb/> return from the states\n                    <del>that</del> you were much surprised<lb/> that you had not reced any account\n                of the annual<lb/> Election of officers to our small congregation, to<lb/> make up\n                therefore for much remisness I now send<lb/> you the names of those elected at\n                our<lb/> meeting and also an account of <persName>Mr DeSola's</persName><lb/>\n                <add>?</add> interesting lecture on the Persecution<lb/> our <sic>bretheren</sic>\n                are suffering in the dominions<lb/> of the <persName>Shah</persName><add>?</add>.\n                You will find some corrections<lb/> in the printed a/c of the lecture which I<lb/>\n                hope you will understand.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I took no notes of the lecture &amp; have not<lb/> read it since but\n                I think what I have<lb/> written <add>?</add> to be quite sufficient for\n                publication<lb/> in a journal devoted to Jewish affairs</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ff3mk73/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
